title: Star Wars Audio Books - Fall of the Republic to Fall of the Empi
description:
This is a release of Star Wars audio books that cover from the collapse of the Republic to the collapse of the Empire. I have removed stories that do not include main characters and add to the movie plots. I have also renamed the files so they are more clearly understood. They are numbered in order in the timeline.

They are as follows:
Cloak of Deception
Shadow Hunder
Phantom Menace
Rogue Planet
Outbound Flight
Way of the Apprentice
Trial of the Jedi
Dangerous Games
Master of Disguise
Approaching Storm
Attack of the Clones
Shatterpoint
Cestus Deception
Jedi Trial
Dark Rendezvous
Labyrinth of Evil
Revenge of the Sith
Dark Lord - Rise of Vader
Paradise Snare
Hutt Gambit
Rebel Dawn
A New Hope
Rebel Mission to Ord Mantell
Empire Strikes Back
Return of the Jedi
Truce at Bakura
